<h1 class="ql-align-justify"><strong>85所高校2020考研报考人数</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201029/fd49f512eeea4208befd275a800a5e06.png" max-width="600" /></p>
